devdoc.details: Implements a voting system with timed release encryption This contract combines vote management with threshold cryptography to ensure votes remain secret until a predetermined time.

exitAsHolder().details: Exit as a secret holder and withdraw deposit

forceExitHolder(address,uint256).details: Force exit a holder who failed to submit shares

params.holderAddress: The address of the holder to force exit
params.voteId: The ID of the vote for which the holder failed to submit a share

getHolderPublicKey(address).details: Get the public key of a holder

returns._0: The public key of the holder

getHolderRewards(address).details: Get the accumulated rewards for a holder

returns._0: The accumulated rewards for the holder

getNumHolders().details: Get the number of registered holders

getNumHoldersByElection(uint256).details: Get the number of registered holders for a specific election

returns._0: The number of holders for the given election

getSubmittedShares(uint256).details: Get submitted shares for a vote

returns.shares: Array of shares submitted by holders
returns.submitters: Array of holder addresses that submitted shares

returns.decryptionTime: The time when the vote can be decrypted
returns.g2r: The G2 point used for share verification
returns.threshold: The minimum number of shares needed for decryption

returns._0: The reward amount for the vote

isHolder(address).details: Check if an address is a registered holder

returns._0: True if the address is a registered holder

joinAsHolder(uint256,bytes).details: Join as a secret holder by staking a deposit

params.publicKey: The BLS12-381 public key of the holder

returns._0: The required deposit amount in wei

submitShare(uint256,uint256,uint256).details: Submit a share for a vote

params.decryptionTime: The time when the vote can be decrypted
params.g2r: The G2 point used for share verification
params.threshold: The minimum number of shares needed for decryption

triggerRewardDistribution(uint256).details: Manually trigger reward distribution for a vote

unJoinAsHolder(uint256).details: Allow a holder who no longer wants to be a secret holder to deregister (assumes no pending votes)
